Welcome to the start of Season Six. A new season, with new wrestlers and amazing unscripted combat. A season that promises everything you have come to love and more.

Ariel X is back after her crushing defeat in the Summer Tournament that denied her the chance to go for the Championship. This setback has caused her to double her efforts and this year she has vowed to be in the championship match up. However right now she needs to [REDACTED] the new girl.

Kirra Lynne comes to US for her first match that clearly won't be her last. She is a fighter. determined never give in or quit. We have found some new great talent for the upcoming season and "The Pit Bull" is one of them

Never was one woman so determined not to get fingered, and never was another so determined to do the fingering as was the case here.
title: Ariel X "The Assassin" (0-0)
